<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.10.5">
<l>kaṇṭavartam maṉammakiḻa māvalitaṉ vēḷvik kaḷaviṉmiku ciṟukuṟaḷāy mūvaṭiyeṉ ṟirantiṭ</l>
<l>ṭaṇṭamumiv valaikaṭalu mavaṉikaḷu mellā maḷantapirā ṉamarumiṭam vaḷaṅkoḷpoḻi layalē</l>
<l>yaṇṭamuṟu muḻavoliyum vaṇṭiṉaṅka ḷoliyu marumaṟaiyi ṉoliyumaṭa vārcilampi ṉoliyum</l>
<l>aṇṭamuṟu malaikaṭali ṉolitikaḻu nāṅkū rarimēya viṇṇakaram vaṇaṅkumaṭa neñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Simple heart, worship in Arimēya Viṇṇakaram in Nānkūr</l>
<l rend="indent">near bountiful gardens where radiate the sound of drums</l>
<l rend="indent">that touches the heavens, the sound of bee swarms,</l>
<l>The sound of the rare Vedas, the sound of ladies’ ankle bells,</l>
<l rend="indent">and the sound of the crashing sea that touches the heavens,</l>
<l>The place where sits the lord who, as a very small dwarf in disguise,</l>
<l rend="indent">having begged at Māvali’s sacrifice, saying, “[Give] three feet,”</l>
<l>Measured all the heavens, these crashing seas, and worlds,</l>
<l rend="indent">so the minds of those who saw [him] rejoiced.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
